reviewText: I ordered both part 1 and part 2 of season 8 and part 2 had 3 of the exact same dvds in it as part 1.  I was ripped off!!!!!!

A+++++ FUNNY AND SERIOUS!!! I like the series finale "The Blair Nurse Project" with the whole "Dick Van Dyke"  family members, it was also a little spooky, just like entering "The Tower of Terror" ride in DisneyWorld or DisneyLand
